<h1><%= @building.name %></h1>
<br>
We are located at: <%= @building.address %>, <%= @building.country %>.
<br>
We have <%= @building.number_of_floors %>floors, and the rent per floor is £<%= @building.rent_per_floor %>.
<br>
The companies which currently live in this building are:
<ul>
    <% @building_companies.each do |company| %>
        <li><%= link_to company.name, company %> | on floor(s): <%= @building.get_floors(company) %>  </li>
    <% end %>
</ul>

This building makes £<%= @building.total_rent %>.

